{"tid":1702992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【TG向TVB跪底，停止抵制TVB頻道】每日洗版任務 -","createTime":"2019-11-10T04:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T23:59:30.000Z","uid":267969,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"fd9b3a2600be3de587d36c453a1609a323a58fb9","tid":1702992,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:59:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">恥笑，TVB真係驚無廣告到仆街</span></strong><br />\n話我哋TG logo侵權，要求TG暫停我哋channel，但TG又真係暫停頻道喎<br />\nIdea is bulletproof<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有種就搞掂埋連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請即follow後備頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb2&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=26f925d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb2</a></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>TG嘅msg喺#2</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>既然TVB咁撚驚洗版<br />\n我哋唔好俾佢停，好唔好？</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【抵制CCTVB 每日任務】</span></strong><br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <br />\n <br />\n是日精選@10 Nov 2019 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>維多C</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RedoxonHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRedoxonHK%2F&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=ae9d01d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RedoxonHK/</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>※記得用留言template</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留言重點</span></strong>係全力阻止廣告商簽訂下年合約</strong> <br />\n<blockquote>無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kXvemeT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkXvemeT.jpg&h=cca74c79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>講下臭屎</strong></span><br />\n成年人建議每日攝取維他命C為90毫克，叫人冲2000毫克嚟飲？飲一杯就已經達到攝取上限喇！小朋友飲仲會超標添！如果之後再食蔬果，長期食過量維他命C咪有機會腎衰歇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實對於預防流感，維他命C的影響極細！做運動同均衡飲食好過啦！咪益無良藥廠！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[Source]<br />\n急補維他命C 有效抗流感？ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2ruYGg3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ruYGg3&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=320211c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2ruYGg3</a><br />\n<br />\n又可以用呢幅圖留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SS8qitc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSS8qitc.jpg&h=49c4d6d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得bookmark</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: TVB廣告客戶名單！！</strong></span> <br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbi