Rj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=a5ad7d3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tvb.com.hk</a> (&quot;Complainant&quot;), App Store and Play Store. Complainant believes your channel <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=4caba1d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a> is infringing its copyright. Please see their comments below.<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\nDear Sirs,<br />\n<br />\nRe: DMCA Notice<br />\n<br />\nWe, Television Broadcasts Limited, are well known television broadcast company in Hong Kong. Television Broadcasts Limited and our group companies (collectively &quot;TVB&quot;) are the copyright owner of various television programmes produced by TVB. TVB is also the registered owner of the following trademarks in Hong Kong and other regions worldwide:<br />\n<br />\n  (&quot;TVB Logo&quot;) and   (&quot;TVBuddy Logo&quot;)<br />\n<br />\nWe have noticed that a Telegram Channel named &quot;CCTVB綜合狙擊頻道&quot; (&quot;Channel&quot;) (URL: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=4caba1d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a> ) has been violating TVB's copyright and trademark by using TVBuddy Logo as its channel logo.  (Please see Annex 1).  In addition, the Channel has been sharing a video footage of a TVB news programme (Please see the attached video) as well as numerous photos that display screenshots of TVB programmes and TVB Logo.  (Please see Annex 2)<br />\n<br />\nWe have good faith belief that the use of the copyrighted materials and trademarks described above as allegedly infringing is not authorized by TVB, its agents, or the law for which TVB is entitled to take legal action against the infringers.<br />\n<br />\nWe understand that you have power under your takedown policy to deal with infringement of third party's copyrights by your users. Please stop the infringement by:<br />\n<br />\n1.            removing or disabling access to the aforesaid copyright and trademark infringed materials immediately; and<br />\n<br />\n2.            terminating the account of the aforesaid Channel.<br />\n<br />\nMy contact details are as follows:<br />\nBy mail: TVB City, 77 Chun Choi Street, Tseung Kwan O Industrial Estate, Kowloon, Hong Kong<br />\nBy fax : (852) 3184 0769<br />\nBy tel. : (852) 2335 2288<br />\nBy email : legal.copyright@tvb.com.hk<br />\nName: Jane Ting<br />\n<br />\nI swear, under penalty of perjury, that the information in the notification is accurate and that I am authorized to act on behalf of the owner of an exclusive right that is allegedly infringed.<br />\n<br />\nYours faithfully,<br />\n<br />\nJane Ting<br />\nSenior Legal Counsel<br />\nTelevision Broadcasts Limited for and on behalf of TVB<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\nTelegram does not process requests related to private content. But sticker sets, channels, and bots on Telegram are publicly available. When we receive a complaint regarding the legality of public content, we perform the necessary legal checks and take it down when deemed appropriate: <a href=\"https://telegram.org/faq#q-wait-0-o-do-you-process-take-down-requests-from-third-parties\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.org%2Ffaq%23q-wait-0-o-do-you-process-take-down-requests-from-third-parties&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=7a0bc7a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.org/faq#q-wait-0-o-do-you-process-take-down-requests-from-third-parties</a><br />\n<br />\nWe kindly ask you to remove the reported content. You can reach <a href=\"http://tvb.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftvb.com.hk&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=a5ad7d3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tvb.com.hk</a> 